column1: #Text=Hey it ’s Jackie and welcome back to my vlog channel .
#Text=We are currently in the car yet again and we ’re driving to Alexander Springs .
#Text=Of course we ’re doing another mermaid photo shoot .
#Text=It ’s not quite summer but it feels like summer here and I never miss a year of mermaid content .
#Text=I really wanted to do something with pearls and do an updo and then have really bronzy makeup .
#Text=And the tail , we have a silicone tail this time , is very similar to this lip tone , and my friend Marianne is staying with us and I love her photography style and styling .
#Text=So she actually made this kind of Grecian top , like , very quickly , and I ca n’t wait to see this location .
#Text=And then after that we are headed to Orlando , I ’m gon na see my parents and we ’re doing Harry Potter World .
#Text=We had to go into this little corner store because um we had to pee and we had to get five dollars worth of stuff .
#Text=Saw this place on the corner of the road .
#Text=Doing some touch-ups before we head into the springs and I ’m using this really beautiful Mac blush , this is the shade Melon Pink .
#Text=For eyes I ’ve been using the Dominique ‘ the Moment Palette ’ .
#Text=I used this in my last video but instead of going with the blues I went with these shades here and I love these together .
#Text=See if I can get you in here .
#Text=I ’m gon na add some to my highlight .
#Text=I ’m gon na go with these rounds under the lash line .
#Text=I feel like we ’re at Mako Island .
#Text=It is so green and the tail is kind of H2O-esque .
#Text=I love how you have your , um –
#Text=Why are you not in – why are you not over there anymore ?
#Text=I ran for my life because I heard a little chirping sound and we already saw the gator warning , so I was like – and threw the tail off , probably good .
#Text=Sorry I did n’t get it on video .
#Text=Where you going – where are you going ?
#Text=But yeah , we ’re packing up and we ’re headed to Orlando .
#Text=You look like you were about to .
#Text=It ’s a very – it was a bird or something , some sort of small –
#Text=It was not a bird , it was a crocodile .
#Text=Jump from one bed to the other , like a child .
#Text=We are all so loopy but I think we are gon na watch a little bit of Harry Potter
#Text=This is the Harry Potter World outfit of the day .
#Text=We did not get up as early as we should have .
#Text=I booked the tickets for the wrong day and that was stressful , but I ended up getting them switched , and we finally made it .
#Text=For the best experience get a park to park ticket so you can do both Hogsmeade and Diagon Alley .
#Text=This was my favorite area in the park , maybe because it was n’t as crowded yet and the wand shop is so epic .
#Text=Everything is really detailed and when you look up even on the way going into the shop there are owls that move up high .
#Text=You know I got ta go with the kid .
#Text=Marianne , which one are you going to get ?
#Text=I do n’t know , I ’m looking at every single one !
#Text=So we got our wands from the shop , and apparently they ’re interactive .
#Text=We do n’t actually know what we ’re doing , but here is my wand .
#Text=I kind of – I do the same motion .
#Text=So we just went on at the Harry Potter and the Forbidden Journey ride .
#Text=You can see that Hogwarts right there .
#Text=And it was so fun , like , I ’m not a rides person , but , um , it felt like you were flying .
#Text=And the wait was n’t even that bad , so yeah .
#Text=With the park to park ticket we took the train to Diagon Alley and for lunch we went to the Leaky Cauldron , which has a bunch of British themed food .
#Text=I would say the food is like a 5 out of 10 .
#Text=It was n’t amazing but it was a really cool spot .
